{"id": "chos024", "name": "Cam_Xenon's_695_10_26", "res": null, "contents": [[{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "Door Opens"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Sherry? Why are you here all of a sudden?\n... Why are you dressed up like this?\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "image", "attrs": ["chos2401"], "content": ""}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "... What happened? Are you crying?\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "<i>*sniff*</i>... no...\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Come inside first.\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Close", "Door Closes"], "content": ""}, {"id": 9, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»» Fast Forward »»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "... Are you going to tell me what happened?\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "...Sorry. I don't want to say anything now.\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Can you just... hug me and don't say anything?\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "... Sure.\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "......\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Hey, sing \"Still\" for me...\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "*I know why they are laughing at us\nI see the sadness spread in your eyes \nonce we were dancing, singing\nsomehow it all changed\nno one else  could understand*\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Haha... your singing sucks.\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "This song was written for you originally... the pitch is too high.\nHow about you sing it.\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Still", "Singing"], "content": ""}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "... Beautiful.\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "The song is very well-written... Lately, when I'm feeling distressed, I'll sing this song. It calms me down.\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "... Is there something that makes you feel distressed?\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "... Simon, There are secrets between us, certainly. But I'm scared at the thought that I'll lose you once you know about them... I'm scared that you can't accept the \"real\" me...\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "... Every person needs secrets. I will not ask you to tell me everything just because we're together. We both agreed to give each other some space, didn't we?\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Yes...\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "It's fine if you tell me when you're ready. No matter what the \"real\" you is, I will always try to accept it, because I treasure this relationship as much as you do.\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "Thank you... you're so kind.\nI still can't tell you everything now, but I will once I'm ready to do so...\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "It's ok. I'll be waiting.\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[Signal Lost]</i>"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "ドアが開く"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Sherry？急にどうした？\nそれに…その恰好なんだよ？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "image", "attrs": ["chos2401"], "content": ""}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……どうしたんだよ？泣いてるのか？\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "うっ…うぅ…泣いてない……\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "とりあえず入れ。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Close", "ドアが閉まる"], "content": ""}, {"id": 9, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»早送り»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……何があったのか話せるか？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……ごめん、今は言いたくない。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "何も聞かずに抱きしめてくれる？\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……分かった。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "………\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "ねぇ、「Still」歌って……\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "*I know why they are laughing at us\nI see the sadness spread in your eyes \nonce we were dancing, singing\nsomehow it all changed\nno one else  could understand*\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "ハハ……へたくそ。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "お前が歌うために作った曲だぞ……\n俺には高すぎる。\nお前が歌え。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Still", "歌声"], "content": ""}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……綺麗な声だ。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "曲がいいんだよ……最近不安な時はこの曲を歌って心を落ち着かせてるんだ。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……何がそんなにお前を不安にしてるんだ？\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……Simon、あたしには秘密がある。\nでも、それをあんたに知られるのが怖い。\n秘密を知ったあんたが、あたしから離れていくんじゃないかって……\n本当のあたしを受け入れてもらえないんじゃないかって……\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……誰にでも秘密はある。\n付き合ってるからって根掘り葉掘り聞くようなことはしない。\n俺らには俺らのやり方があるだろ？な？\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "うん……\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "心の整理ができてから、俺に話してくれればいい。\n本当のお前がどうであろうと、受け入れる気持ちでいる。\n受け入れられるように努力する。\n俺だって、お前を失うのは怖い。\n大切にしたいんだ。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "ありがとう……Simonは優しいね。\nでも、やっぱり今はまだ話せない。\nその時が来たら、絶対に話すから……\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "いいよ。待ってる。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[電波切断]</i>"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Sherry？怎麼突然跑來？\n……妳這身打扮是怎麼回事？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "image", "attrs": ["chos2401"], "content": ""}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……怎麼啦？妳在哭？\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "嗚……沒有……\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "先進來吧。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Close", "關門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 9, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……妳要告訴我發生什麼事了嗎？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……對不起，我現在不想說。\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "可以就這樣抱著我什麼都不要說嗎？\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……可以。\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "吶，唱「Still」給我聽……\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "*I know why they are laughing at us\nI see the sadness spread in your eyes \nonce we were dancing, singing\nsomehow it all changed\nno one else  could understand*\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "哈哈……你唱得好爛。\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "這首本來就是寫給妳唱的啊……太高了啦。\n那妳唱。\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Still", "歌聲"], "content": ""}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……好好聽。\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "你寫得很棒啊……最近不安的時候只要唱這首歌，心情就會平靜下來。\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……有什麼讓妳感到不安的事嗎？\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……Simon，我想說我們之間是存在祕密的，但我怕讓你知道了會失去你……怕你不能接受真正的我……\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……每個人都需要祕密，我不會因為我們在一起就刨根究底的，我們都有給彼此空間的默契，不是嗎？\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "嗯……\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "等妳準備好了再跟我說也沒關係，無論真正的妳是如何，我都會試著去接受，因為我也跟妳一樣珍惜這段感情。\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "謝謝……你真好。\n我還是沒有辦法現在就告訴你，不過等我準備好我一定會說的……\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "沒關係，我等妳。\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[訊號中斷]</i>"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "문이 열린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Sherry? 왠일이야 갑자기?\n무슨 일이야?\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "image", "attrs": ["chos2401"], "content": ""}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……무슨 일이야? 우는 거야?\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "하아…… 아니야……\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "우선 들어와.\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Close", "문이 열린다"], "content": ""}, {"id": 9, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»빨리 감기»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……무슨 일인지 얘기 안 할 거야?\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……미안. 지금은 얘기하고 싶지 않아.\n"}, {"id": 12, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 13, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "그냥... 지금처럼 아무 말 없이 안아주고만 있어줘....\n"}, {"id": 14, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……알았어.\n"}, {"id": 15, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 16, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……\n"}, {"id": 17, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "나, 「Still」 듣고 싶어… 불러줘.\n"}, {"id": 18, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "*I know why they are laughing at us\nI see the sadness spread in your eyes \nonce we were dancing, singing\nsomehow it all changed\nno one else  could understand*\n"}, {"id": 19, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "하하…… 노래 완전 못해.\n"}, {"id": 20, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "이 노래 원래 너한테 주려던 곡이라고...\nkey가 너무 높아. \n아니면 네가 불러 보던지.\n"}, {"id": 21, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Still", "노랫소리"], "content": ""}, {"id": 22, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……잘 부르네.\n"}, {"id": 23, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "네가 노래를 잘 써줘서 그렇지..... 최근 불안할 때마다 이 노래만 부르고 있어. 부르고 나면 마음이 좀 나아지는 것 같거든.\n"}, {"id": 24, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……뭐가 널 그렇게 불안하게 만드는 거야?\n"}, {"id": 25, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……Simon. 사실 아직까지 네게 말하지 못한 게 있어. 하지만 네가 알게되면..... 진짜 나의 모습을 받아들이지 못할까봐....\n"}, {"id": 26, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……누구나 비밀 하나쯤은 가지고 살아가. 사귄다고 해서 모든 얘기를 다 해야 한다는 법은 없으니깐. 우리는 우리들만의 방식이 있잖아. 안 그래?\n"}, {"id": 27, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "응……\n"}, {"id": 28, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "마음의 준비가 되면, 그때 얘기해. 진정한 네 모습이 무엇이든, 난 다 받아들일 수 있도록 노력할 거니깐. 그리고 나 역시도 널 잃는 걸 원치 않아.\n"}, {"id": 29, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "고마워…… 그렇게 말해줘서.\n지금은 네게 말할 수 없지만 \n나중에 준비가 되면... 꼭 말할게.\n"}, {"id": 30, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "그렇게 해. 기다릴게.\n"}, {"id": 31, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[신호 중단]</i>"}], [{"id": 0, "type": "bgm", "attrs": ["MUTE"], "content": ""}, {"id": 1, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Open", "開門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 2, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "Sherry？怎麼突然跑來？\n……妳這身打扮是怎麼回事？\n"}, {"id": 3, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……。\n"}, {"id": 4, "type": "image", "attrs": ["chos2401"], "content": ""}, {"id": 5, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……怎麼啦？妳在哭？\n"}, {"id": 6, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "嗚……沒有……\n"}, {"id": 7, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "先進來吧。\n"}, {"id": 8, "type": "sound", "attrs": ["Xenon's_Door_Close", "關門"], "content": ""}, {"id": 9, "type": "text", "attrs": [], "content": "<i>[»»»快轉»»»]</i>\n"}, {"id": 10, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Xenon"], "content": "……妳要告訴我發生什麼事了嗎？\n"}, {"id": 11, "type": "conversation", "attrs": ["Cherry"], "content": "……對不起，我現在不想說。\n"}, {"id"